# Configurator MVP context

Before changing configurator UX or 3D behavior, read **`docs/CONTEXT.md`**.

## Volvo reference (flow only — keep our dark industrial skin)

https://www.volvotrucks.es/es-es/tools/truck-builder.html#/es-es/configurator/fh16aero

Mirror: wizard steps, tray cards with selected state, Volver/Siguiente, live summary bar, hero product + side preview.

## Hard constraints

- `BuildConfig` in `ConfiguratorShell` = single source of truth (no Zustand/backend)
- Keep `ModelViewerClient` `dynamic(..., { ssr: false })`
- Keep grid layout and dark slate/cyan look
- Chassis color dominates; finish is surface (matte/hi-vis/chrome), not a full repaint
- Modules = glow feedback; no IR/LIDAR hotspot labels on the helmet
- No prices in UI for now; no real PDF
- No new dependencies unless asked
- Addons/agregados = future geometry (separate assets/slots), not another material tint
